{"tid":930372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今時今日仲要撘狗鐵真係畜生嚟","createTime":"2018-12-06T09:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T09:52:37.000Z","uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"43abe495198d7f089546c9c72c5a46785d1a1d00","tid":930372,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T09:25:46.000Z","msg":"一車車豬迫埋一齊咁運<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：坐開司機車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa4919a102e892b9714612014474304d4695895e","tid":930372,"uid":205645,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T09:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a5pNGR9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa5pNGR9.jpg&h=440e0ad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nThis one?"},{"pid":"94ae1783f00c356f1b9cd1e5cb0408ecc401b73a","tid":930372,"uid":170601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa4919a102e892b9714612014474304d4695895e","tid":930372,"uid":205645,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T09:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a5pNGR9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa5pNGR9.jpg&h=440e0ad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nThis one?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T09:41:02.000Z","msg":"原來樓主日日坐呢架車，<br />\n唔通樓主係仵作?"},{"pid":"6e85bf707416b81cd6ccfb715b8d4e4c5c2f3896","tid":930372,"uid":50707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T09:47:56.000Z","msg":"做跟車仲要大大聲同人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d9d937771acccac61c6e17ae3f3823d94959bd","tid":930372,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T09:48:17.000Z","msg":"向來喜歡獨來獨往的梁朝偉，早前就被本刊獨家捕獲，以一身熱爆冒險遊戲《看門狗》（Watch Dogs）之男主角的殺手look，到佐敦廟街漫遊，再乘搭港鐵過海，逛金鐘超市格價購物，一餐晚飯也消費不過二百元；就算其間到過HMV揀選影碟，亦齋睇唔買。身家豐厚的「影壇第一男神」，其實都可以好慳家！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/tmp_images/article_multimedia/43417/1_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Ftmp_images%2Farticle_multimedia%2F43417%2F1_n.jpg&h=b555584f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車廂內，梁朝偉把帽子壓得更低，並埋首於手機屏幕中，身邊乘客也發現不到「影帝」的大駕光臨。他使用的手機是iPhone 6 Plus，價值$8,088。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/43417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Fmain%2F43417&d=xfoDiEkTl4ylQGsgb%2F9wvU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=51bb8cff\" target=\"_blank\">https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/43417</a>"},{"pid":"4d2b6aab9eb8f9f53cecc21dc51d443c077eac78","tid":930372,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T09:50:25.000Z","msg":"某日下午，周潤發以一副超cool勁型Mark哥黑超look，現身中環搭港鐵去尖沙咀買越野跑鞋，過程中不少港人都認出發哥，但最終只有少數幾人成功「捕獲野生發哥」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/tmp_images/resources/73567/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Ftmp_images%2Fresources%2F73567%2F1.jpg&h=15f19adf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/73567\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Fmain%2F73567&d=xfoDiEkTl4ylQGsgb%2F9wvU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=3299eefa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/73567</a>"},{"pid":"78b792adf1c25f6d4b3965b11a301b471c10ac9b","tid":930372,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T09:51:30.000Z","msg":"講到最鍾意坐港鐵嘅，就非周潤發莫屬，經常都畀網民野生捕獲。其實發哥好樂意同大家Selfie，仲會自己主動揸埋機，自拍技術相當好！不過講真，發哥都曾經話，有時佢搭嗰陣都冇乜人見到，因為個個掛住睇手機。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180809/mobile/bkn-20180809210058904-0809_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180809%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180809210058904-0809_00862_001.html&d=xfoDiEkTl4ylQGsgb%2F9wvU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=8a73c6c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180809/mobile/bkn-20180809210058904-0809_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ada84ab05712e86a3934f9680d819743daad6b9f","tid":930372,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T09:52:37.000Z","msg":"每日返工放工都搭東鐵頭等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}